Homecoming wasnt what i expected but it was fun! Lol...Now i cant feel my feet...haha...And my chariot was my uncles old truck...it was ghetto and i listened to "in the ghetto" by Elvis on the way there. And the before party was funny. Tricia recorded me becky and ryan singing stupid songs...we watched Veggie Tales and Forrest Gump... It was fun. I hated my dress though...but oh well...im pooped..later!
after school today, I fell down all of my trailers stairs after 6th period...Im in serious pain and i also broke the railing

That was our WORST competition EVER! Seriously, only ONE 1...and that was for Drum Major and they also got 3rd place Drum Major in the class...ugh....

i REALLY want to quit band, or least marching band..

Band Camp sucked yesterday.....
Now 4 more days of band for this week...ahhhh.....

 

Anywho, Life sucks...

Im signing up for the sat now...it sucks...

Band practice was horrible today...Magner had us March through the whole show in the rain...and certain people were getting on my nerves and then on the way home....a certain person talked about their homecoming group and they were like "Who are you going with?" And i was like a bunch of freshmen because things didnt work out...I STILL LOVE YOU FRESHIES! But yeah, it made me depressed...
Then today i got 3 tests back and failed 2 and got a c on the other. Highest grade out of those tests was a 79 and the lowest was a 29...arg...
Bad Day

So this week hasnt been a good week AT ALL! 1) The car broke down 2) My dad moved out 3) My 17 year old"friend" is pregnant 4) The ONLY guy that i REALLY wanted to go to homecoming with got himself another date. Which sucks...now i dont have anyone to go to homecoming with for my senior year....5) I failed a test...

I dont know...

Life Sucks

Get a Helmet

So i am still feeling like crap. I went to Kristens surprise party for like a hour then left...tomorrow i have a 5 year old birthday party to go too.
I went back to the doctor today to see what my xray results were. After waiting 2 hours, he said that my xrays looked fine, BUT he wants me to go see a back doctor next week because he is really concerned about my back. It still hurts like crap. The pain wont go away. Its been OVER a MONTH! AHHH!!! + this stupid head cold....

What did i do to deserve this?
Keep praying para me....please? I need some love!
My back has been bothering me for about a month and i am having tests on it.

Just wanna say one thing...

FIRST WEEK WAS SO MUCH FUN!!!!

thats all for now.

I tend to get on peoples nerves SSSSSSSSSSSOOOOOOOOOOOO much that i lose them as a friend. So then when i need help on something that only they can help on...i have no more friends...Im sorry to those who i did that to. I try to be a caring person who loves all her friends very much. But some of them just dont want that love. And i cant do anything about it. I suck as a friend. And im sorry to those who i have gotton on their last nerve. Just to let all of those people and to the ones that "cant stand me". I still love yall and im always here if you need a friend...

Alright i said my peace...now, i got to find this homework on here and get to bed....I CANT FIND A ESSAY TOPIC FOR MY COLLEGE CHOICE! AHHH!!

Anyone have these classes?

And if i die this semester...I love yall...

Last week at Junalska was fun too. Hung out with Zoar/Harmony Grove people. Got CRAZZZZZY at the dance on thursday night. (You certain people, you know you liked it!) haha...so now im tired. Yall can message me or call me! Aight....lata! 770-402-0250!

I promise ill update when i get back!
Adios!

Thats all i wanted to be just once was some kind of band officer. But no. Im really upset right now. I need some love.... :-( This was the PERFECT ending to the PERFECT week. 

Am i annoying? My friend told me that people come up to him and tell him that Im annoying....
I want the truth...please tell me?

So yeah, random story for the day...

So this morning i was wearing this BIG PUFFY LIGHT BLUE COAT, right? So, i went to my bus stop at 6:40, 5 minutes before my bus actually comes.So yeah i watched my bus go down the street turn around in the culdasac(sp?) come up and SPEED past my bus stop. I was like "WHAT THE FOO?"" (Jennifer that is SO my phrase! :)) And i started jumping up and down,while my bus was passing me. He didnt see me.So, i ran as fast as i could up the hill to the next bus stop. I have NEVER ran that fast before in my life, not even in basketball games. So yeah i was like "ZIA TELL HIM TO WAIT!!!" like 5 times before the girl at that bus stop got on, but she didnt hear me...I was like "FOO!" So i ran back down the hill i just ran up, cut through 4 backyards to two streets over to catch the bus over there. Im like have really bad sinuses right now so by the time i got over there, my chest hurt really bad, and i couldnt really breathe. Bad part was that the stop i got on, there was a REALLY HOT GUY that gets on there. And i was really embarressed. OMG to the E*POINT! So my bus gets to that stop and i got on and my bus driver looked at me kinda funky and i was like, "You know you sped right by me at my stop right?" And he was like " I slowed down and looked for you and didnt see you." WHATEVER! He didnt even slow down, AT ALL! So this afternoon right before i got off the bus i said "Thanks for remembering my stop." And i walked right off the bus...hehe

So had a LATE basketball game tonight against some ex-varsity Parkview basketball players....wow, it was close....NOT! 45-19. hehe...I scored 10 of those 19 points...yeah buddy...

Festival band rehearsal tomorrow...

My grandma's cousin is getting married tomorrow AT my grandma's house...how retarded is that?( I have my reasons)

MATT RUCKER IS GAY! hehehe 

Valentines Day is tomorrow, and for the 16th year in a row, i dont have a "valentine". hehehe....This day sucks....

Hope yalls is good though!

I miss Matt...

So yeah i hate this time of year because i have no one to enjoy it with...

Today my church were handing out Valentine Day balloons where you had to buy one before today for a special someone. And pretty much everyone in my Sunday School class got at least one...except for me.Even my brothers got one.So yeah, im unloved...hahaha..and im sure Tuesday at school is going to be similiar to today. 

Friday night i babysat some kids with Leslie Fowler at my church.We both got $30 bucks...sweet...Afterwards we went to CVS and saw Jennifer Waller...I drove myself too...which was fun. 

Saturday I went to go see "Bye Bye Birdie" at Berkmar High. My friend Elena was in it so i went to support her. Saw some kids from Parkview which was cool. The "Conrad Birdie" in it has an AMAZING voice. He sounded just like Elvis, it was so creepy and cool.When he first started singing, i didnt believe it was his real voice. And he was "kinda" cute.His character was like a Elvis wannabe type too, and he was GREAT at it.

Anyways im going to go back to reading my book. Mr. Darcy is just falling in love with Miss Elizabeth Bennet in "Pride and Prejudice".But i cant seem to get into the book...I like the movie...

So yall are now reading the journal of an official...
 Georgia Driver....

I hit two cones and i messed up one other time but other than that....

I PASSED!

OMG...hopefully by this time tomorrow i will be a liscensed Georgia driver...I really cant see myself doing this...Im so incredibly nervous...I will let you know tomorrow how it went...omg...i cant do this...im afraid im going to mess up on something really easy...I tried again at parallel parking today and backing into a parking spot...and i sucked...i cant do this....Oh lord give me strength from thine own hand...please....i really need to get this liscense tomorrow....yall please pray for me....omg...omg...omg....This is obviously me nervous...im shaking...I think im going to fail...im so freaking nervous...

So yeah Im sick...thats why im missing out on my best friends birthday party.....So now i feel bad, because i said some mean things to him yesterday because we were in a fight....I feel like crap now...health and emotional wise

I went to the "HAWKS vs. ORLANDO MAGIC" game tonight with my dad...it was very interesting. We got club sits...which was cool. And guess who was there?

CHRIS TUCKER AND EMMANUAL LEWIS

Pretty cool stuff....

Afterwards me and my padre went to Waffle House where i saw a couple of my friends from school...Now its bed time...

Hawks won by the way with .7 seconds left in the game, tied up..and BAM...Hawks made a two pointer....

96-94...

yeah

So, yeah, been really busy with school. Stressed out about different things. Today i stayed after school to get help with Unit 9 in Music theory and mr. magner was like " if you need anymore help just come to my office." And when i needed help he had disappeared. So i waited till jazz band was over and asked mr. beach. Mr. Beach and Mr. Magner think im obsessed about music theory because i HAVE to get a 100 on it and everytime i miss one, i start over. I ended up getting a 98, because after awhile i just said SCREW IT!I missed one. I still have another section to do, before next week. So much for my 100 in that class. You dont know how many times i restarted that unit....it was getting me MAD!

So right now i have a 101.88 in SS. I ended up getting a 102 on the last test.I thought i screwed up/ i knew i screwed up on the essay...but he didnt count it. Oh well.

Well, time for a couple of hours of sleep before i have to get up and do stuff...as of right now...im completely stressed out and tired. Hopefully my stressoutness will be over after i get my liscense next wednesday.

Dude..this weekend was definetly not what i expected and definetly what i needed in my life right now. 

Friday- We arrive at lake junalska and we get room assignments. I ended up rooming with Amanda Fergusen and Hannah Davis. 

Saturday- Woke up early and went to breakfast with the skiers, ( i was not one of them) and came back to the lodge and got ready for the day. The people who did not go sking went shopping in downtown Waynesville. Came back and had a little nap. Skiers came back around 5 and we all went to dinner and then had devotion. After devotion we came back to the lodge and my roommates straightened my hair and put make up on me... Hannah dragged me to the boys room against my will....hehehe...(Who is going to straighten my hair on retreats from now on...?) and then I fell and hurt my elbow real bad.

Sunday- Slept in, and went to morning devotion. Came back and got ready to see a movie. Saw "Cheaper by the Dozen 2" with some people. I was torn between movies or playing football with everybody else. Im glad i chose movie because everyone got bruised up. Kevin wanted me to play football and Tori wanted me to see a movie. oh well...Came back and freshened up and then went to dinner and then night time devotion. I got really close to some of the people. Went back to the lodge and ended up getting sick. Everyone went to Waffle House/Huddle House while i stayed back and slept.I fell asleep watching "Pretty Woman".

Monday- Woke up, washed my hair and then packed. Put stuff out in trailer and hung out till we were ready to go. Left about 10. Slept all the way home

Fun Times....

My Devotion Group: Me, Robert, Kevin, Melissa, Justin, Derek, Evan, Mr. B., Mr. Yates, Josh.

Awesome Group...

What a freaking amazing game...yeah we lost...but we were winning up until the last 2 minutes of the game...29-26. Im happy to say that i scored 4 points...go me....and i got ALOT of rebounds....dude...I flipped a girl over my shoulder...it was SWEET...well not for her. I had the ball and she was all over my back and i went down to guard it from her and the next thing i knew she had gone over me and landed on the floor. This girl was as big as me too...it was awesome. I HAVE NEVER SEEN A TEAM FALL AS MUCH AS THEM!!! i swear..everytime i turned around...one of their players were on the ground. Especially that girl i flipped...She fell constantly. My coach said she is nice and all but can be VERY dramatic. Our 4'2 90 something pound girl "bumped" into her and she went down. She faked alot of falls. The refs were also calling no fouls. But hey...we played a tough game...and it was one of the funnest i have ever played. Both teams were VERY AGGRESSIVE...My brother said he has never seen ANY girl team as violent as the teams that played tonight. Hey,a girls got to do what a girls got to do. 

Shower Time

I have a basketball game tonight.....fun stuff....i have never been so hyper today in my life....I laughed at everything.....for 3 STRAIGHT CLASSES! hahahaha...all i had was a bottle of coke. I drank it 2nd period and then didnt talk 3rd period and laughed  4,5,6 period...GO HOPE!!!

;-D
My mom told me today that i suck at singing...Now im never going to sing again. On top of that today was just a plain out bad day.Hope yalls are better
Its the second day of the new year and so far i have done nothing but lay around and sleep. Its time for some MAJOR changes...
I feel like crap right now. I think i have a fever...and my tummy hurts...to much shit going on
